♪Time and space brought me
to another yellowed page♪

30
00:01:25,470 --> 00:01:26,830
♪Sunlight pierces through♪

31
00:01:26,830 --> 00:01:28,560
♪One comes and goes as one pleases♪

32
00:01:28,560 --> 00:01:30,140
♪My Go board holds both sides♪

33
00:01:30,140 --> 00:01:31,870
♪When I set the game, learn to see♪

34
00:01:31,870 --> 00:01:33,530
♪Don't be a sore loser♪

35
00:01:33,530 --> 00:01:35,010
♪So many lies and deceits♪

36
00:01:35,010 --> 00:01:36,890
♪I can see through every play♪

37
00:01:36,890 --> 00:01:38,440
♪May I live and die
with the sun♪

38
00:01:38,620 --> 00:01:41,180
=Guardians of the Dafeng=

39
00:01:41,340 --> 00:01:44,140
=Episode 38=

40
00:01:44,240 --> 00:01:45,240
Summon the Cabinet

41
00:01:45,310 --> 00:01:46,550
to the court immediately

42
00:01:46,550 --> 00:01:48,470
for Duke Huai's Bloodshed Case.

43
00:01:48,670 --> 00:01:49,510
Yes.

44
00:01:53,550 --> 00:01:54,390
Lin'an,

45
00:01:54,750 --> 00:01:55,830
what's the emergency?

46
00:01:56,470 --> 00:01:57,310
Brother,

47
00:01:58,520 --> 00:01:59,720
Father won't admit...

48
00:02:03,240 --> 00:02:04,270
He won't admit

49
00:02:05,190 --> 00:02:06,110
Uncle created

50
00:02:06,270 --> 00:02:08,640
the bloodshed in Chuzhou, will he?

51
00:02:11,360 --> 00:02:12,200
Brother...

52
00:02:14,800 --> 00:02:15,800
Don't forget who you are.

53
00:02:16,480 --> 00:02:17,550
This isn't your concern.

54
00:02:18,670 --> 00:02:19,960
Can't you be like Huaiqing?

55
00:02:20,200 --> 00:02:21,040
She's been silent.

56
00:02:23,040 --> 00:02:23,880
Why?

57
00:02:24,670 --> 00:02:26,800
Isn't it true that Uncle killed those people?

58
00:02:26,800 --> 00:02:27,640
Shut up!

59
00:02:38,110 --> 00:02:38,950
Lin'an,

60
00:02:41,870 --> 00:02:43,110
Father adores you

61
00:02:43,590 --> 00:02:44,870
because you're a sweet girl,

62
00:02:45,390 --> 00:02:47,040
and you never interfere in state affairs.

63
00:02:49,480 --> 00:02:50,320
But now,

64
00:02:51,960 --> 00:02:53,390
how come you've changed?

65
00:02:56,640 --> 00:02:57,830
Are you getting involved

66
00:02:59,320 --> 00:03:00,670
because of Xu Qi'an?

67
00:03:01,110 --> 00:03:02,270
He incited you, didn't he?

68
00:03:02,390 --> 00:03:03,550
He didn't do anything.

69
00:03:05,480 --> 00:03:06,960
I haven't seen him for days.

70
00:03:16,800 --> 00:03:17,920
I can't see him.

71
00:03:19,150 --> 00:03:20,390
I feel guilty.

72
00:03:22,760 --> 00:03:24,520
Duke Huai is my uncle.

73
00:03:26,520 --> 00:03:28,960
He committed such atrocities in Chuzhou.

74
00:03:29,150 --> 00:03:30,200
We're family.

75
00:03:30,200 --> 00:03:31,760
How could I stay out of this?

76
00:03:39,590 --> 00:03:40,480
So

77
00:03:40,870 --> 00:03:42,110
did you ask to see me

78
00:03:42,760 --> 00:03:43,710
to make me

79
00:03:44,320 --> 00:03:45,670
remonstrate with Father?

80
00:03:50,710 --> 00:03:52,240
Father wouldn't see you,

81
00:03:53,920 --> 00:03:55,110
let alone me.

82
00:04:02,360 --> 00:04:03,200
Lin'an,

83
00:04:04,590 --> 00:04:06,360
there's no right or wrong in court.

84
00:04:06,590 --> 00:04:08,040
Only gains and losses matter.

85
00:04:08,330 --> 00:04:10,320
Whether or not my words
carry weight is one thing.

86
00:04:12,990 --> 00:04:14,150
As the Crown Prince,

87
00:04:15,360 --> 00:04:17,000
I must stand four-square

88
00:04:17,120 --> 00:04:18,910
with the nobility and imperial clansmen.

89
00:04:21,640 --> 00:04:22,680
You're a princess.

90
00:04:23,350 --> 00:04:24,910
No one cares about what you do.

91
00:04:26,290 --> 00:04:27,150
Were you a prince,

92
00:04:27,150 --> 00:04:28,640
those words of yours would cost you

93
00:04:29,470 --> 00:04:31,030
your chance of coming to the throne.

94
00:04:31,790 --> 00:04:33,790
But he murdered so many people.

95
00:04:35,250 --> 00:04:36,420
Hundreds of thousands of them!

96
00:04:38,080 --> 00:04:39,560
Shouldn't he pay for their deaths?

97
00:04:40,560 --> 00:04:42,880
Or who'd be in awe of the Dafeng royalty

98
00:04:43,350 --> 00:04:45,230
and the law of the Dafeng?

99
00:04:45,470 --> 00:04:47,470
There were, there are, and there will be

100
00:04:47,470 --> 00:04:48,710
tons of such things.

101
00:04:55,000 --> 00:04:56,590
Once Father makes the decision,

102
00:04:56,590 --> 00:04:57,760
no one can change it.

103
00:05:03,440 --> 00:05:04,470
Listen, silly,

104
00:05:05,390 --> 00:05:07,000
Father's throne was

105
00:05:09,150 --> 00:05:11,120
built on bones and blood.

106
00:05:18,880 --> 00:05:20,120
If we didn't come,

107
00:05:20,350 --> 00:05:22,710
our imperial image
built in the last 600 years

108
00:05:22,710 --> 00:05:25,760
would be ruined by you.

109
00:05:26,000 --> 00:05:26,910
My Lord,

110
00:05:27,270 --> 00:05:29,680
Duke Zhenbei killed
all the people of Chuzhou.

111
00:05:30,440 --> 00:05:34,150
Those 380,000 souls need justice.

112
00:05:34,520 --> 00:05:38,080
Everyone else in our state needs justice.

113
00:05:39,000 --> 00:05:41,060
(Duke Cheng, Imperial Clansman)
After the Battle

114
00:05:41,080 --> 00:05:42,760
of Linyuan Pass, Duke Zhenbei was ordered

115
00:05:43,120 --> 00:05:44,880
to guard the northern border.

116
00:05:45,030 --> 00:05:46,320
Now that he's dead,

117
00:05:46,760 --> 00:05:48,030
can't we keep

118
00:05:48,030 --> 00:05:49,440
his posthumous name intact?

119
00:05:50,080 --> 00:05:51,830
His merits can't offset his crimes.

120
00:05:52,270 --> 00:05:53,110
Your Majesty,

121
00:05:54,030 --> 00:05:56,230
it's true that he safeguarded our state,

122
00:05:56,590 --> 00:05:59,960
but it's also true
that he was guilty beyond forgiveness.

123
00:05:59,960 --> 00:06:01,030
He shall be punished.

124
00:06:01,030 --> 00:06:02,500
Your Majesty, Wang Zhenwen

125
00:06:02,500 --> 00:06:04,780
(Duke Lu, Imperial Clansman)
is defaming a duke in public.

126
00:06:04,780 --> 00:06:05,890
That's a capital crime.

127
00:06:05,990 --> 00:06:06,760
Dukes,

128
00:06:07,150 --> 00:06:09,390
think carefully about this case.

129
00:06:09,620 --> 00:06:11,390
(Duke Li, Imperial Clansman)

130
00:06:11,390 --> 00:06:12,560
You're a lowly eunuch.

131
00:06:12,790 --> 00:06:15,470
Without His Majesty's appreciation,

132
00:06:15,470 --> 00:06:17,790
you wouldn't have the right to speak here.

133
00:06:20,960 --> 00:06:23,560
I'm grateful for Your Majesty's kindness.

134
00:06:24,390 --> 00:06:25,230
However,

135
00:06:25,470 --> 00:06:28,230
for the sake of the imperial image,

136
00:06:28,440 --> 00:06:29,280
the Dukes

137
00:06:29,440 --> 00:06:31,470
shouldn't try to cover up this case.

138
00:06:32,000 --> 00:06:34,440
Yesterday, the three masters of the Academy

139
00:06:34,680 --> 00:06:35,710
meant to come

140
00:06:36,030 --> 00:06:37,390
to rebuke Your Majesty.

141
00:06:39,230 --> 00:06:40,470
I stopped them.

142
00:06:40,760 --> 00:06:41,600
They said

143
00:06:42,030 --> 00:06:42,880
now that

144
00:06:43,270 --> 00:06:45,470
Duke Huai killed the people of Chuzhou,

145
00:06:45,680 --> 00:06:46,520
the Academy

146
00:06:46,830 --> 00:06:49,350
would write down his crimes

147
00:06:49,830 --> 00:06:51,120
in history

148
00:06:51,200 --> 00:06:52,270
to warn future generations.

149
00:06:52,270 --> 00:06:53,830
How the Dukes

150
00:06:54,120 --> 00:06:55,880
covered for him today

151
00:06:55,960 --> 00:06:57,440
would also be engraved in it

152
00:06:57,960 --> 00:06:59,440
in full detail.

153
00:07:01,880 --> 00:07:02,760
Duke Li,

154
00:07:04,150 --> 00:07:05,960
you've always been proud

155
00:07:05,960 --> 00:07:06,960
and erudite.

156
00:07:07,150 --> 00:07:08,790
You're a role model for Imperial Clansmen

157
00:07:08,790 --> 00:07:11,350
and every student in the state.

158
00:07:12,230 --> 00:07:13,560
Would you rather see

159
00:07:14,120 --> 00:07:15,640
the Yunlu Academy write down

160
00:07:16,320 --> 00:07:18,640
how you covered for a murderer

161
00:07:19,390 --> 00:07:21,000
and be condemned forever?

162
00:07:21,320 --> 00:07:23,030
How dare you threaten me!

163
00:07:23,120 --> 00:07:24,440
Are you being rebellious?

164
00:07:25,000 --> 00:07:27,440
When did advice become a threat?

165
00:07:27,560 --> 00:07:28,400
You...

166
00:07:31,960 --> 00:07:32,830
All of you...

167
00:07:39,520 --> 00:07:40,360
Your Majesty,

168
00:07:40,520 --> 00:07:41,790
permission to speak.

169
00:07:42,910 --> 00:07:43,910
Simu said,

170
00:07:43,920 --> 00:07:45,560
His Majesty held a sudden meeting earlier

171
00:07:45,560 --> 00:07:47,120
to discuss Duke Huai's Bloodshed Case.

172
00:07:47,120 --> 00:07:48,560
How did it go? What's the conclusion?

173
00:07:49,230 --> 00:07:50,560
Officials didn't win,

174
00:07:50,830 --> 00:07:52,320
but neither did His Majesty.

175
00:07:53,120 --> 00:07:55,230
The debate would drag on and on.

176
00:07:55,640 --> 00:07:56,680
Unexpectedly,

177
00:07:56,760 --> 00:07:58,150
State Duke Cao stepped forward

178
00:07:58,150 --> 00:07:59,270
to speak up.

179
00:07:59,680 --> 00:08:00,520
Your Majesty,

180
00:08:01,440 --> 00:08:03,990
over the years, we've been
having internal and external troubles.

181
00:08:04,030 --> 00:08:05,150
People have been struggling.

182
00:08:05,230 --> 00:08:07,440
Tax arrears keep building up.

183
00:08:07,680 --> 00:08:10,150
Despite your unceasing tax cuts

184
00:08:10,150 --> 00:08:11,440
to ease people's burden,

185
00:08:11,680 --> 00:08:14,390
complaints are heard everywhere.

186
00:08:15,320 --> 00:08:16,350
At this time,

187
00:08:16,520 --> 00:08:19,590
if they knew about the bloodshed,

188
00:08:20,120 --> 00:08:23,120
what would they think about the court?

189
00:08:23,590 --> 00:08:26,790
What would squires and petty officials think?

190
00:08:27,560 --> 00:08:28,910
Would they think

191
00:08:29,030 --> 00:08:30,590
the court was hopeless

192
00:08:31,000 --> 00:08:32,960
and do worse

193
00:08:32,960 --> 00:08:34,630
in exploiting the people

194
00:08:34,630 --> 00:08:36,560
even more brazenly?

195
00:08:36,560 --> 00:08:37,440
How bold!

196
00:08:40,680 --> 00:08:43,400
Are you calling me fatuous

197
00:08:44,870 --> 00:08:46,110
and the officials

198
00:08:46,440 --> 00:08:48,440
blind and incompetent?

199
00:08:48,870 --> 00:08:50,200
I wouldn't dare.

200
00:08:52,040 --> 00:08:54,960
But aren't the officials

201
00:08:55,080 --> 00:08:57,510
acting as if they're blind and incompetent?

202
00:08:57,920 --> 00:09:00,040
They keep shouting

203
00:09:00,040 --> 00:09:01,590
to uphold justice for the people

204
00:09:01,590 --> 00:09:02,830
and convict the culprit now.

205
00:09:03,830 --> 00:09:06,080
Has anyone considered the bigger picture?

206
00:09:06,630 --> 00:09:08,110
As court officials,

207
00:09:08,110 --> 00:09:10,470
don't you know the image of the court

208
00:09:10,470 --> 00:09:12,680
also represents your image?

209
00:09:14,320 --> 00:09:15,510
But Duke Zhenbei

210
00:09:17,440 --> 00:09:19,800
was indeed guilty.

211
00:09:19,920 --> 00:09:20,960
Your Majesty,

212
00:09:21,560 --> 00:09:22,590
Duke Zhenbei is...

213
00:09:23,200 --> 00:09:25,470
is already dead.

214
00:09:26,040 --> 00:09:28,710
Can death erase everything?

215
00:09:28,710 --> 00:09:29,710
Yes.

216
00:09:29,990 --> 00:09:32,750
Chuzhou was harassed by Kui for years.

217
00:09:32,870 --> 00:09:34,830
The city fell into ruin.

218
00:09:35,320 --> 00:09:36,750
When Kui seized it,

219
00:09:36,750 --> 00:09:38,560
Duke Zhenbei put up a desperate struggle,

220
00:09:38,710 --> 00:09:40,110
battling the chief of Kui alone.

221
00:09:40,110 --> 00:09:41,800
He killed the Mighty Bone

222
00:09:41,800 --> 00:09:43,200
and guarded the gate of the Dafeng

223
00:09:43,200 --> 00:09:44,800
to the end.

224
00:09:45,080 --> 00:09:46,470
He fell with the city

225
00:09:46,470 --> 00:09:48,160
and died heroically!

226
00:09:49,320 --> 00:09:50,320
After that war,

227
00:09:50,630 --> 00:09:52,560
Chuzhou will enjoy over ten years

228
00:09:52,830 --> 00:09:54,870
or tens of years of peace.

229
00:09:56,710 --> 00:09:57,550
Your Majesty,

230
00:09:57,560 --> 00:09:59,230
he died a worthy death.

231
00:09:59,400 --> 00:10:01,400
He's a hero of the Dafeng!

232
00:10:02,470 --> 00:10:03,350
Your Majesty!

233
00:10:05,320 --> 00:10:06,200
State Duke Cao,

234
00:10:07,470 --> 00:10:08,830
did you forget

235
00:10:09,400 --> 00:10:12,960
not only I witnessed the bloodshed?

236
00:10:13,440 --> 00:10:14,280
The...

237
00:10:15,230 --> 00:10:16,990
the mission,

238
00:10:17,510 --> 00:10:19,990
those 20,000 troops in Chuzhou,

239
00:10:20,080 --> 00:10:24,040
and the people in the capital all know it!

240
00:10:24,590 --> 00:10:25,430
Can you...

241
00:10:25,830 --> 00:10:26,670
can you...

242
00:10:27,080 --> 00:10:30,680
can you keep all of them quiet?

243
00:10:41,320 --> 00:10:44,110
They used the images of the court and royalty

244
00:10:44,340 --> 00:10:46,560
and the chief of Kui's death as leverage.

245
00:10:47,160 --> 00:10:48,400
Although Chuzhou fell,

246
00:10:48,630 --> 00:10:50,440
that was all Kui's fault.

247
00:10:51,510 --> 00:10:52,750
What a wonderful chain.

248
00:10:52,990 --> 00:10:53,990
It sounds reasonable.

249
00:10:55,750 --> 00:10:56,830
In that case,

250
00:10:56,960 --> 00:10:59,750
the fall of Chuzhou wouldn't be intolerable.

251
00:10:59,750 --> 00:11:01,990
It happened all because of war

252
00:11:01,990 --> 00:11:03,110
and Kui.

253
00:11:03,320 --> 00:11:04,870
Duke Huai would turn from a murderer

254
00:11:05,320 --> 00:11:07,160
to a hero and guardian of the Dafeng

255
00:11:07,990 --> 00:11:10,110
who even killed the chief of Kui.

256
00:11:10,470 --> 00:11:11,560
That was a great merit.

257
00:11:15,350 --> 00:11:16,190
- Wait!
- Wait!

258
00:11:16,320 --> 00:11:17,160
You first, Ningyan.

259
00:11:18,160 --> 00:11:19,280
This plan wasn't too bad,

260
00:11:19,350 --> 00:11:21,320
but it'd hold the officials back at most.

261
00:11:21,320 --> 00:11:22,750
The sharp ones could easily tell

262
00:11:22,750 --> 00:11:23,870
that was His Majesty's show.

263
00:11:23,870 --> 00:11:24,710
Correct.

264
00:11:24,830 --> 00:11:26,680
Mr. Zheng's last line is the point.

265
00:11:26,830 --> 00:11:28,710
Many people know about the bloodshed.

266
00:11:29,080 --> 00:11:30,800
Could such a self-deceiving show

267
00:11:30,800 --> 00:11:32,470
silence everyone?

268
00:11:32,830 --> 00:11:35,320
He started paving the way a long time ago.

269
00:11:35,710 --> 00:11:37,110
He knew it couldn't.

270
00:11:37,630 --> 00:11:38,470
Was all this

271
00:11:39,630 --> 00:11:41,200
also to lay the groundwork?

272
00:11:42,280 --> 00:11:43,200
Does His Majesty have

273
00:11:43,870 --> 00:11:44,920
more cards up his sleeve?

274
00:12:12,800 --> 00:12:14,400
After Duke Huai died,

275
00:12:15,200 --> 00:12:17,800
the North lost the sky-propping pillar.

276
00:12:18,560 --> 00:12:21,750
Kui can't stir up more trouble,

277
00:12:22,230 --> 00:12:23,080
but

278
00:12:23,630 --> 00:12:25,040
The Witcher's Sect

279
00:12:25,510 --> 00:12:26,750
can go around

280
00:12:27,110 --> 00:12:29,160
Chuzhou

281
00:12:29,710 --> 00:12:31,750
and head straight to the capital

282
00:12:32,400 --> 00:12:33,920
to deal a death blow.

283
00:12:37,710 --> 00:12:40,160
The sky-propping pillar is too big

284
00:12:41,470 --> 00:12:42,630
and hard to control.

285
00:12:43,510 --> 00:12:45,230
Once it falls,

286
00:12:46,440 --> 00:12:47,470
it'll be

287
00:12:48,800 --> 00:12:49,800
lose-lose.

288
00:12:52,560 --> 00:12:53,400
Is that so?

289
00:12:55,200 --> 00:12:56,400
Your Majesty,

290
00:12:56,920 --> 00:12:58,590
reports from every palace said

291
00:12:59,110 --> 00:13:00,710
no one was harmed.

292
00:13:01,320 --> 00:13:02,800
Nothing was stolen.

293
00:13:05,870 --> 00:13:07,510
Has the assassin been seized?

294
00:13:08,080 --> 00:13:08,990
Your Majesty,

295
00:13:11,280 --> 00:13:12,120
not yet.

296
00:13:12,230 --> 00:13:14,200
Keep looking.

297
00:13:14,200 --> 00:13:15,040
Yes.

298
00:13:18,590 --> 00:13:20,320
An assassin broke in?

299
00:13:21,560 --> 00:13:22,400
Why

300
00:13:22,920 --> 00:13:24,230
didn't I know?

301
00:13:26,470 --> 00:13:28,590
I kept it quiet, telling them

302
00:13:28,590 --> 00:13:30,230
not to make a fuss.

303
00:13:31,280 --> 00:13:32,750
It happened suddenly,

304
00:13:32,990 --> 00:13:34,990
causing panic in the Palace.

305
00:13:37,750 --> 00:13:39,040
Even the Empress

306
00:13:40,870 --> 00:13:43,800
was frightened.

307
00:13:53,230 --> 00:13:55,830
The assassin must be caught quickly

308
00:13:56,750 --> 00:13:59,320
to put an end to this matter.

309
00:14:00,920 --> 00:14:01,760
The Empress

310
00:14:03,680 --> 00:14:06,230
can stop worrying.

311
00:14:09,990 --> 00:14:11,320
Your chess skills

312
00:14:13,710 --> 00:14:15,750
have further advanced, Your Majesty.

313
00:14:19,230 --> 00:14:20,470
Are you giving up?

314
00:14:25,920 --> 00:14:26,760
Another around.

