322
00:15:06,350 --> 00:15:07,560
I'm tired.

323
00:15:08,750 --> 00:15:10,110
So are you.

324
00:15:14,680 --> 00:15:18,630
I implore you to convict Duke Zhenbei!

325
00:15:51,320 --> 00:15:52,160
Mr. Zheng.

326
00:15:53,440 --> 00:15:54,590
Wait, Mr. Zheng.

327
00:15:55,510 --> 00:15:56,350
Mr. Zheng,

328
00:15:56,630 --> 00:15:58,100
you left Chuzhou without permission

329
00:15:58,110 --> 00:15:59,360
to seek justice in the capital,

330
00:15:59,620 --> 00:16:01,540
thinking you'd win for sure.

331
00:16:01,620 --> 00:16:02,960
Did you think

332
00:16:03,130 --> 00:16:04,300
you'd end up like this?

333
00:16:06,140 --> 00:16:08,160
Here's my advice.

334
00:16:08,680 --> 00:16:09,520
Mr. Zheng,

335
00:16:12,680 --> 00:16:14,590
Chuzhou has been destroyed.

336
00:16:14,710 --> 00:16:16,200
You should stay there

337
00:16:16,460 --> 00:16:18,040
to rebuild the city.

338
00:16:18,540 --> 00:16:19,800
Stay out of

339
00:16:20,440 --> 00:16:22,110
the things in the capital.

340
00:16:23,320 --> 00:16:25,630
That's also His Majesty's thought.

341
00:16:42,280 --> 00:16:44,230
You're shameless.

342
00:16:44,630 --> 00:16:46,710
What can I do?

343
00:16:53,110 --> 00:16:54,440
That old geezer.

344
00:16:54,960 --> 00:16:56,230
How stupid!

345
00:16:57,510 --> 00:16:59,080
When you came back

346
00:16:59,990 --> 00:17:01,800
to report on your work after the inspection,

347
00:17:02,560 --> 00:17:05,200
we met once.

348
00:17:05,470 --> 00:17:06,710
Back then,

349
00:17:07,160 --> 00:17:08,960
you were gray-haired

350
00:17:09,550 --> 00:17:11,880
but vigorous.

351
00:17:14,070 --> 00:17:14,960
Lord Wei,

352
00:17:15,470 --> 00:17:17,470
are you also giving up?

353
00:17:17,960 --> 00:17:19,030
Xu Qi'an

354
00:17:19,440 --> 00:17:20,790
is a valuable talent.

355
00:17:21,400 --> 00:17:22,440
I believe

356
00:17:22,790 --> 00:17:24,990
he's a born Fighter.

357
00:17:26,030 --> 00:17:30,360
His temper and character
can give me a headache, though.

358
00:17:31,070 --> 00:17:32,230
I told him

359
00:17:33,200 --> 00:17:35,880
to survive in the official circles,

360
00:17:36,230 --> 00:17:37,550
think about three things.

361
00:17:38,710 --> 00:17:39,710
Danger,

362
00:17:40,310 --> 00:17:41,360
retreat,

363
00:17:42,070 --> 00:17:43,030
and change.

364
00:17:44,360 --> 00:17:45,750
Before taking action,

365
00:17:46,230 --> 00:17:48,360
think about the consequences

366
00:17:48,750 --> 00:17:50,470
and what's involved.

367
00:17:50,840 --> 00:17:52,840
Weigh the pros and cons

368
00:17:53,270 --> 00:17:54,550
before engaging in

369
00:17:55,360 --> 00:17:56,600
or giving up.

370
00:17:57,230 --> 00:18:00,230
If you can't stop what's coming your way,

371
00:18:00,790 --> 00:18:01,960
then retreat.

372
00:18:02,680 --> 00:18:03,960
Take a step back.

373
00:18:07,840 --> 00:18:10,790
But Xu Qi'an said,

374
00:18:11,790 --> 00:18:12,640
"Lord Wei,

375
00:18:13,640 --> 00:18:15,840
I understand all that,

376
00:18:16,750 --> 00:18:17,640
but

377
00:18:18,160 --> 00:18:19,310
I don't care."

378
00:18:21,200 --> 00:18:22,840
What a boorish Fighter.

379
00:18:28,270 --> 00:18:31,440
If you call him "boorish",

380
00:18:31,600 --> 00:18:36,120
that means you can't change him.

381
00:18:36,750 --> 00:18:38,310
Step back

382
00:18:39,510 --> 00:18:40,750
to be safe.

383
00:18:41,310 --> 00:18:42,470
When you're safe,

384
00:18:42,990 --> 00:18:44,310
you can think about

385
00:18:44,790 --> 00:18:46,750
how to change the situation.

386
00:18:47,840 --> 00:18:50,990
There's still room to turn the tide.

387
00:18:51,680 --> 00:18:52,710
Mr. Zheng,

388
00:18:53,750 --> 00:18:55,680
why not take a step back

389
00:18:56,750 --> 00:18:58,360
and take things slow?

