Commissioner of Chuzhou, Zheng Xinghuai,

392
00:19:50,840 --> 00:19:52,680
would like to see Prime Minister Wang.

393
00:19:53,200 --> 00:19:56,070
He's with a guest at the moment.

394
00:19:56,070 --> 00:19:58,790
He won't be able to see you soon.

395
00:19:59,030 --> 00:20:00,030
Commissioner Zheng,

396
00:20:00,270 --> 00:20:01,550
