00:20:15,030 --> 00:20:15,870
Sir.

398
00:20:20,030 --> 00:20:21,880
Go to the Secretary of War's Mansion.

399
00:20:22,470 --> 00:20:23,310
Yes.

400
00:20:24,180 --> 00:20:28,140
(Wang Mansion)

401
00:20:31,380 --> 00:20:33,740
(Ministry of War)

402
00:20:40,680 --> 00:20:41,520
Sir.

